            </a>
            <a href="/switching-lenders-at-renewal" class="rounded-lg p-4" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
              <p class="font-semibold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--primary)">Switching Lenders at Renewal</p>
              <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">No stress test for straight switches since 2024. Save thousands.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/mortgage-renewal-checklist" class="rounded-lg p-4" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
              <p class="font-semibold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--primary)">Mortgage Renewal Checklist</p>
              <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">Step-by-step from 120 days before to signing day.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/mortgage-renewal-mistakes" class="rounded-lg p-4" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
              <p class="font-semibold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--primary)">10 Biggest Renewal Mistakes</p>
              <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">Including auto-renewing and choosing rate type based on emotion.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/mortgage-broker-renewal" class="rounded-lg p-4" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
              <p class="font-semibold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--primary)">How a Broker Helps at Renewal</p>
              <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">Free to use, accesses 30+ lenders including monolines.</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
