            <a href="/book-a-call" class="block w-full text-center rounded-lg py-2 font-semibold text-sm" style="background: var(--secondary)">
              Book a Free Call
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg p-5" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--primary)">The Rate Hold Strategy</h3>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">Start 120 days early. Lock in a rate. If rates fall, your broker can often access the lower rate. You get downside protection with upside opportunity.</p>
